{"title":"荐歌：盛夏（毛不易）","slug":"荐歌：盛夏（毛不易）","date":"2022-07-01T10:14:48.000Z","updated":"2022-07-01T10:15:54.601Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/荐歌：盛夏（毛不易）.json","excerpt":"文章来自微信公众号“科文路”，欢迎关注、互动。转发须注明出处。周末愉快！","covers":null,"content":"<blockquote>\n<p>文章来自微信公众号“科文路”，欢迎关注、互动。转发须注明出处。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>周末愉快！</p>\n<iframe frameborder=\"no\" border=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" width=330 height=86 src=\"//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=569212211&auto=1&height=66\"></iframe>\n\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<p>连续的高温天气真是恼人啊！听说下周成都的气温甚至会冲上 40℃，还真是不寻常。</p>\n<p>这不由得就想起了毛不易的这首《盛夏》。</p>\n<p>伴随着毛氏温情声线，悠扬的曲调和美好的歌词景象就在脑海婉转起来。</p>\n<p>“铁道旁的老树下，几只乌鸦”、“火车呼啸着驶过，驶过寂寞或繁华”这些不多的场景描述却异常深刻，引人入胜。</p>\n<p>周末找个地方玩水吧~别因为热就被锁在屋里啦！</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">作词 : 毛不易</span><br><span class=\"line\">作曲 : 毛不易</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">那是日落时候轻轻发出的叹息啊</span><br><span class=\"line\">昨天已经走远了</span><br><span class=\"line\">明天该去哪啊</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">相框里的那些闪闪发光的我们啊</span><br><span class=\"line\">在夏天发生的事</span><br><span class=\"line\">你忘了吗</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">铁道旁的老树下</span><br><span class=\"line\">几只乌鸦</span><br><span class=\"line\">叫到嗓音沙哑</span><br><span class=\"line\">却再没人回答</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">火车呼啸着驶过</span><br><span class=\"line\">驶过寂寞或繁华</span><br><span class=\"line\">曾经年轻的人啊</span><br><span class=\"line\">也想我吗</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">就回来吧，回来吧</span><br><span class=\"line\">有人在等你呢</span><br><span class=\"line\">有人在等你说完那句说一半的话</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">就别走了，留下吧 </span><br><span class=\"line\">外面它太复杂</span><br><span class=\"line\">多少次让你热泪盈眶却不敢流下</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">可时光啊，不听话，总催着人长大</span><br><span class=\"line\">这一站到下一站旅途总是停不下</span><br><span class=\"line\">就慢慢的，忘了吧，因为回不去啊</span><br><span class=\"line\">这闭上眼睛就拥有了一切的盛夏</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><strong>都看到这儿了，不如关注每日推送的“科文路”、互动起来~</strong></p>\n<p><strong>至少点个赞再走吧~</strong></p>\n","more":"<p>连续的高温天气真是恼人啊！听说下周成都的气温甚至会冲上 40℃，还真是不寻常。</p>\n<p>这不由得就想起了毛不易的这首《盛夏》。</p>\n<p>伴随着毛氏温情声线，悠扬的曲调和美好的歌词景象就在脑海婉转起来。</p>\n<p>“铁道旁的老树下，几只乌鸦”、“火车呼啸着驶过，驶过寂寞或繁华”这些不多的场景描述却异常深刻，引人入胜。</p>\n<p>周末找个地方玩水吧~别因为热就被锁在屋里啦！</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span